    #{@trip_pass.researcher.name} has accepted #{@trip_pass.user.name}'s trip request!
%p
  #{@trip_pass.researcher.name} has accepted #{@trip_pass.user.name} trip request from #{@trip_pass.dateStart}
  to #{@trip_pass.dateEnd} at #{@trip_pass.location} for #{@trip_pass.researcher.name}'s research: #{@trip_pass.research.name}

%p
  Please contact
  %strong
    #{@trip_pass.user.name}
  at
  %strong
    #{@trip_pass.user.phone_number}
